node.text:
Get your computer feeling just like new again. ⚡️#CCleaner is our go-to multi-device tool to make our computers run cleaner, faster and safer - helping them to last longer!

PLUS -  Their all-new Health Check feature​ offers a 4 in-1 tool to boost ​privacy​, ​clear disk space​ (by deleting unnecessary files), ​increase speed​ (by disabling programs you don’t need) and ​security​ (by updating outdated apps to close security holes.) Oh, and did we mention it’s FREE.

🔗 Link in bio to learn more!

#CCleanerHealthCheck #CCleanerSpringClean
